{"tid":263953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"港姐競選造勢 朱千雪人氣勁 麥明詩冇人理!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-05-30T12:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T07:03:29.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa58cf1f1ddd07a4a334d27126b8eb738f915e4e","tid":263953,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2017-05-28_23-27-37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F2017-05-28_23-27-37.jpg&h=2a44ddd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港姐競選又開始接受報名，早前無綫找來朱千雪、陳凱琳（Grace）、馮盈盈、麥明詩等一班師姐到中環天星碼頭呼籲靚女參選，集眾靚女之力，簡直是示範何謂「靚爆鏡」！不過一大班靚女同場，難免會有比較。據《e+娛樂》報道稱，出名敢言、網上勁多支持者的麥明詩，活動結束後一支公行去搭船，夠晒貼地，惜沿途居然未有被市民認出！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2017-05-28_23-27-29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F2017-05-28_23-27-29.jpg&h=28b5dba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相比之下，朱千雪就因為太多粉絲跟身，寸步難行，未知是否跟麥明詩沒有着裙仔有關呢？<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2017-05-28_23-27-25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F2017-05-28_23-27-25.jpg&h=7f1aceed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2017-05-28_23-27-33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F2017-05-28_23-27-33.jpg&h=ae0ed329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好在Grace的人氣也不弱，在等候的士期間，獲一眾師奶圍住影合照的她亦來者不拒。其間，Grace更遭粉絲捉實手臂，她仍繼續保持笑容逐個影完才離開。"},{"pid":"69be14f32a5f6b44c95200804e6f3bd53f9f7e34","tid":263953,"uid":69256,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:20:51.000Z","msg":"點解麥明詩好似靚咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3cef9ac6b3f172f05d1ded1f04142